title: Bösentrift
text: The Bösentrift is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the <a href="Pennine%20Alps">Pennine Alps</a>, overlooking <a href="T%C3%A4sch">Täsch</a> and <a href="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> in the canton of <a href="Valais">Valais</a>. It lies north of the <a href="Oberrothorn">Oberrothorn</a>.
